OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772381500
OL,3,CTrain crash scene was like 'giant had
OL,4,Cstamped on a toy set', says widow
OL,6,FThe driver of the car, Gary Hart, had
OL,7,Fbecome drowsy at the wheel when he
OL,8,Fcrashed into the embankment and was
OL,9,Flater sentenced to five years for
OL,10,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
OL,12,FSpeaking about the morning of the
OL,13,Fcrash 25 years on, Mary said: "I went
OL,14,Fdownstairs. I think the boys had
OL,15,Falready put the television on and the
OL,16,Ffirst picture I saw was of a train
OL,17,Fcrash."
OL,19,FShe remembers being told the news by
OL,20,FStephen's colleagues.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
