PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772381500
OL,3,CTrain crash scene was like 'giant had
OL,4,Cstamped on a toy set', says widow
OL,6,F"I remember I heard a scream and
OL,7,Frealised it was me. And then someone
OL,8,Fsaid, 'give her a brandy it's good for
OL,9,Fshock'. I hate brandy, but it did sort
OL,10,Fof take the feeling away."
OL,12,FDescribed as the worst rail disaster
OL,13,Fof the 21st century, the Great Heck
OL,14,Ftrain crash killed ten people and left
OL,15,Feighty others with life changing
OL,16,Finjuries.
OL,18,FMary likened the scene to if "a giant
OL,19,Fhad kicked a train set then stamped on
OL,20,Fit", with debris strewn everywhere
OL,21,Facross adjacent fields.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
