PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772381500
OL,3,CTrain crash scene was like 'giant had
OL,4,Cstamped on a toy set', says widow
OL,6,F"You wouldn't have thought a real
OL,7,Ftrain could look like that."
OL,9,FA quarter of a century on, survivors
OL,10,Fand loved ones of those killed have
OL,11,Fvowed never to forget the disaster.
OL,13,FMore than 1,000 emergency service
OL,14,Fpersonnel from Yorkshire and
OL,15,Fneighbouring counties responded to the
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
