PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772381500
OL,3,CTrain crash scene was like 'giant had
OL,4,Cstamped on a toy set', says widow
OL,6,FSpeaking at a memorial garden erected
OL,7,Fat the scene of the tragedy, Mary said
OL,8,Fshe still remembers the noise of the
OL,9,Fgenerators used as emergency services
OL,10,Fworked to pull survivors from the
OL,11,Fwreckage.
OL,13,F"I don't think I'll ever forget it.
OL,14,FAnd I don't think I should forget it
OL,15,Fbecause it's coloured my life from
OL,16,Fthereon in."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
