CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772381500
OL,3,CTrain crash scene was like 'giant had
OL,4,Cstamped on a toy set', says widow
OL,6,FSurvivor Bob Brook's life was also
OL,7,Fchanged forever by the crash, after
OL,8,Fescaping death by inches when
OL,9,Ftravelling on the Kings Cross-bound
OL,10,Fpassenger train to catch a Eurostar
OL,11,Ffor a holiday.
OL,13,FThe impact left Bob with eight broken
OL,14,Fribs, causing severe internal bleeding
OL,15,Fwhich, doctors said, would have caused
OL,16,Fhim to die had he arrived at the
OL,17,Fhospital only 30 minutes later. He
OL,18,Falso sustained head injuries which may
OL,19,Fimpact him later in life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
