PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772381500
OL,3,CTrain crash scene was like 'giant had
OL,4,Cstamped on a toy set', says widow
OL,6,F"Some of those head injuries are
OL,7,Fcoming back to me now to haunt me," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"Getting back to going on the train
OL,11,Fafterwards was extremely hard. Now I
OL,12,Fhave no problem but I still, everytime
OL,13,FI go past Heck, look out of the window
OL,14,Fand think about things.
OL,16,F"I've been back there every year
OL,17,Fexcept two since the accident."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
